createContracts(string,string,string,str.details: Creates a new StandardDAO and TreasuryContract pair.

params._daoDescription: A brief description of the DAO.
params._daoDiscordAccount: The Discord account of the DAO.
params._daoOnlyMembersCanPropose: Flag indicating if only members can create proposals.
params._daoXAccount: The X (Twitter) account of the DAO.
params._initialWhitelistedFunders: An array of initial whitelisted funder addresses for the TreasuryContract.
params._initialWhitelistedTokens: An array of initial whitelisted token addresses for the TreasuryContract.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
